{"tid":1520424,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"分手邊緣","createTime":"2019-08-30T19:33:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-02T14:10:54.000Z","uid":66059,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"604a9ce8f92ea058ca83d80ffc0f8b2f2c2e9085","tid":1520424,"uid":66059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T19:33:10.000Z","msg":"之前同女朋友都嘈咗幾個月，佢一直話要啲時間諗同考慮。但係到而家都一段時間，佢仲考慮緊，咁即係點？<br />\n同埋佢之前話我有野做得唔好，咁我咪跟住去改，但佢又話我突然咁轉令佢覺得好恐怖，好似同緊第2個拍拖咁，唔係同我同一個人。佢咁講即係點<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"379948cd3fa0e930795cdfcebe01ec08ea317659","tid":1520424,"uid":33930,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T19:33:31.000Z","msg":"幾句講哂<br />\n831宗教集會 港島見<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">901 1點鐘 機場見</span></span><br />\n92大三罷<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OvNBCkd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOvNBCkd.jpg&h=f0ee9ddd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">記住啊 我地只係幫機管局做交通壓力測試</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">901 機場 Channel</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=7zzHsEpI0SCc5dEpMOtc2ahYowssEfWxGXKUUX6%2FcpY%3D&h=9d1ba6a9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">901 機場 公海</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=7zzHsEpI0SCc5dEpMOtc2ahYowssEfWxGXKUUX6%2FcpY%3D&h=f41bf305\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">901 機場 宣傳</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><a href=\"http://t.me/stuck